\fIgl:validateProgramPipeline\fR\& instructs the implementation to validate the shader executables contained in \fIPipeline\fR\& against the current GL state\&. The implementation may use this as an opportunity to perform any internal shader modifications that may be required to ensure correct operation of the installed shaders given the current GL state\&.
